            <section class="pt60 pb60 grayBg">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="flexBox partnerInfo">
                        <div class="text">The University of Science and Technology presides the list of a number of
                            local and international institutions as an effective international partner, and contributor
                            to a number of medical, and educational institutions including the following:
                        </div>
                        <ul class="list">
                            <li>The Association of Arab Universities</li>
                            <li>Arab higher education institutions</li>
                            <li>Federation of the Universities of the Islamic World</li>
                            <li>The International Association of Universities</li>
                            <li>The Arab Network for Open and Distance Education</li>
                            <li>Member of the International Council for Open and Distance Education (ICDE)</li>
                            <li>Member of the International Computer Driving License (ICDL).</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
